			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "To trigger Greetings (HasMet)\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. Use bebug book > Location > Act 1 > UND > Duergar Camp\r\n4. Finish first dialog.\r\n5, Talk to Cleric Morghal.\r\n\r\nTo trigger Nere Killed\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. Use bebug book > Location > Act 1 > UND > Duergar Camp\r\n4. Finish first dialog.\r\n5, Use Recon command: \"SetGlobalOsirisFlag UND_TheDrowNere_State_Dead\"\r\n6. Talk with Cleric Morghal\r\n\r\nTo trigger Mutiny happened\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. Use bebug book > Location > Act 1 > UND > Duergar Camp\r\n4. Finish first dialog.\r\n5, Use Recon command: \"SetGlobalOsirisFlag UND_DuergarCamp_State_Mutiny\"\r\n6. Talk with Cleric Morghal\r\n\r\nTo trigger Greeting (Deepgnome tag)\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. Use bebug book > Location > Act 1 > UND > Duergar Camp\r\n4. Finish first dialog.\r\n5, Use Recon command: \"addTag DEEPGNOME:2bbc3217-3d8c-46e6-b599-a0f1c9063f9a\"\r\n6. Talk with Cleric Morghal.\r\n\r\n"
				},
